assets.description:
I pushed one of my character sketches a ways further, developing it into a larger scene which I've recently added to my VR Chat world. It fits quite nicely within my dark and abstract environment. 

My world should be live in VR Chat next week (PC Steam game). If you want to jump and climb on it, join the "Surreal Hazard" world within the game. You can find this Blocks model near the foot of the largest mountain.

assets.name: assets/dulZUSpI30q
assets.description:
Model by Juraj Kos
The culmination of many months of anatomy study, this is a representation of a female musculoskeletal structure that directly affects the outer shape of the body.

Huge thanks to Ryan Kingslien for his expansive, in-depth anatomy course, especially the muscle sculpting parts. Also, a big thanks for making a similar model available with Zbrush, from which I’ve taken the skeleton for this project.

assets.name: assets/bviTR_dzM0n
assets.description: This scene was painted using intuitive gestures, while listening and responding to Donald Byrd's Clarion. The modal color scheme and discontinuous marks resemble the trumpeter's compositional style during the early 1960's.
